title: Infinity interfaces and chest preset
descriptionMarkdown:
## Introduction
This is a blueprint of an **infinity chest** with set filters for the cheat-mode items **infinite electricity, fluids and unloaders**.
Every time I want to create blueprints, I keep forgetting the commands to insert an infinity chest. Since, by default, these cheat interfaces aren't available from the inventory GUI, I use this for quick access.

## how to set up
- make sure cheat mode is on with  ```/c game.player.cheat_mode=true``` or by starting a sandbox game and enabling cheat mode.
- place this blueprint
- press `Q` (or your `Settings>Controls`>`Basic interaction`>`pipette tool` keybind) on the [ghost](https://wiki.factorio.com/Ghost) of this blueprint
- enjoy.

### more sandbox stuff
I tried making a [little compendium a while back](https://www.factorio.school/view/-L7BnkM6kTxgOFpMWU6b). It contains some deprecated blueprints to quickly setup robots with access to every item for fast blueprint building. (To actually quickly test your blueprints in the vanilla game)
